      "name": "Shadow Clone Jutsu",
      "type": "spell",
      "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-pentagon-orange.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>You create shadow clones of yourself that are physical copies capable of independent action.</p><p>You create <strong>1d4 shadow clones</strong> of yourself in unoccupied spaces within 30 feet of you. Each clone has the following properties:</p><ul><li>AC equal to 10 + your Dexterity modifier</li><li>1 hit point</li><li>Speed equal to yours</li><li>Can take the Attack, Dash, Disengage, Dodge, or Help action</li><li>Attacks use your attack bonus and deal 1d4 + your ability modifier damage</li></ul><p>The clones act on your turn and last for 1 minute or until destroyed. When a clone is destroyed, it disappears in a puff of smoke.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> When you cast this jutsu at a higher rank, you create additional clones: B-Rank (2d4), A-Rank (3d4), S-Rank (4d4).</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
